Security Engineering Jobs-
Security Engineer
Includes-
+ All from SOC jobs and Information Security Analyst jobs
+ System Health checks like checking dashboards on various tools 
+ configuring and managing security tools
+ system hardening or patching
+ Security Architecture & Design
+ Code review for security weaknesses.
+ Application security
+ Analysis of compromised systems

Skills required-
+ All from SOC jobs and Information Security Analyst jobs
+ System hardening
+ Cryptography, certificates, tls, ssl, key management
+ IAM
+ DevSecOps for ci/cd pipelines and sdlc



Cloud Security Engineer/Specialist
Includes-
+ Cloud infra. security
+ IAC security
+ IAM
+ using cspm and siem
+ access control
+ security policy and groups
+ data protection in rest and transit
+ VPC security
+ Security Automation & DevSecOps like CI/CD pipeline and Ansible, Terraform,etc.
+ Threat Detection & Incident Response using cloud tools.
+ Compliance & Governance
+ Vulnerability and Risk Management
+ Automation of security tools

Skills-
+ Frameworks and attack techniques
+ Cloud Fundamentals expert
+ Cloud Security Services
+ IAM
+ Cloud network security
+ Encryption & Key Management
+ Threat Detection & Response
+ IAC 
+ CI/CD Pipeline Security
+ Vulnerability Management
+ Risk assessment
+ Compliance & Governance



Information Systems Security Engineer
Includes-
+ All from SOC jobs and Information Security Analyst jobs
+ Incident Support and Response helping SOC and incident response team.
+ Implementing Security Solutions like full step-ups of security tools if need from scratch
+ Forensics and Recovery like post attack/incident/alert analysis
+ Patch Management Coordination
+ Automation

Skills-
+ Skills all from security engineer and basic skills from cloud security
+ RCA


